Starting the weekend right by wishing a very Happy Mothers day to some of the greatest cat mums under #thewoofagency network! 🐱⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
You have entered a long journey of sharing your desk, being a servant to your fur kid and waking up to random noises at night. 😹⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
But always remember that they love you very much because you’ve given them a place to call home. ❤️✨⁣
⁣
Stay tuned for part 2 and 3 tmr! 🔆 ⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
